query:
UPDATE sites 
SET floorLevelId = (
  SELECT id FROM floor_levels 
  WHERE centreId = (SELECT id FROM shopping_centres WHERE name = 'Campbelltown Mall') 
  AND levelName = 'Test Upper Level'
)
WHERE centreId = (SELECT id FROM shopping_centres WHERE name = 'Campbelltown Mall')
AND siteNumber IN ('Site 2 (Upper Level)', 'Site 7 (Upper Level)');
